---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Blog & Technical Writeups
description: Thought leadership, deep technical walkthroughs, and security research.
---

<header class="page-header">
    <div class="container">
        <h1 class="gradient-text">{{ title }}</h1>
        <p>{{ description }}</p>
    </div>
</header>

<main class="blog-details">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="blog-intro">
            <h2 class="tech-section-title" style="justify-content: center;">My Security Philosophy</h2>
            <p>I believe security is a continuous process of proactive hunting, rigorous detection engineering, and structured investigation. In these writeups, I share my technical approach to solving complex SOC challenges and dissecting modern threats.</p>
        </div>

        {% for post in collections.blog | reverse %}
        <article class="technical-card blog-post-card">
            <div class="meta-info">{{ post.data.category }} â€¢ {{ post.date | postDate }}</div>
            <h2 class="tech-section-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
            <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
            
            <div class="hero-cta" style="margin-top: var(--spacing-md);">
                <a href="{{ post.url | url }}" class="btn btn-secondary">Read Full Writeup</a>
            </div>
        </article>
        {% endfor %}
    </div>
</main>
